{"h099ec3f4g23d6g44f8gbf62gbc726ad0bf59": ["Do you hear them? The birds. They're beautiful. ", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "333a4f76-ab9e-9790-e91e-811eec968c1e"], "he4209b40g509bg42efga771g78f2d4b24442": ["I've thought of nothing but goblins and tieflings for so long, I stopped listening.", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "f28dfd9c-c839-37e4-ad38-078fb0ae498c"], "h2d8d7a66g0913g4772ga9d5g0e3fdab5b3de": ["The grove feels safe again. We have you to thank for that.", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "73ddf158-b546-8fe5-30c2-3ce0fcf206c4"], "h39619d4ag4502g4256gbee2g6dcd43d17789": ["I know you had to stop her, but Kagha was just trying to protect us.", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "6b6df2f0-cc74-0232-8f74-fc00d6a366dd"], "h4229120cg11fbg432eg8cd1g269f0847a175": ["What are we doing to do now? She's gone. Master Halsin's missing. We're exposed.", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "0dbb5957-8ccb-7efd-9b7e-09850b0106d5"], "hf55e3597gd7b7g446eg9027g9cc3b37972c1": ["She went too far, but at least she had a plan.", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "ae0ce772-7b40-6926-a914-a2c4f67f4788"], "h69ba94bdgd711g4de8gaea4gafa2b6733de6": ["You get to move on. We're stuck here, defenceless.", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "c3906df7-cdfe-0f81-0755-1f656f815d6e"], "h0b77c623g1d86g4395g9e75gc63219386fc0": ["<i>In umbram cretus, sanguine iuratus.</i>", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "eeb64cee-22bc-7374-6327-b0fdb8e9c158"], "h776670b6g9757g4e08gbaf0gaa8046c3c158": ["<i>Ab spiritu humoque, aculeus vitisque.</i>", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "26a69d13-b61b-d2ac-64d1-5e1bf386f39e"], "hec4dab97g6f49g4d36g89eeg817766a314af": ["<i>Complexum tuum, ab terra ortum, ad nos defer.</i>", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "a2f271c5-c256-88c7-3304-0119a96680e5"], "h5d59bf75g343ag419cg8c9bg9c8fbfdd287a": ["<i>Defende nos ab imminentibus aequilibrio tuo.</i>", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "fb856a87-b693-4691-0b4f-fec6ee270173"], "h8a6f4d23g3686g429dga0a7gb7f2a98a7d4e": ["<i>Hostes subeunt. Protege nos. Muni nos.</i>", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "d8ac9adb-58aa-25a9-b6c0-8e4bcdf7a145"], "h22a2a8bbg6a8cg42e2gb4bdgd6e8b72c7ac7": ["<i>Aggeniculamur in umbra tua, Pater Arborum.</i>", "32bef45a-47ca-4c3a-b907-13a857b316fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid4.html", "4582b804-7eb1-8619-8bd1-63a44eb1338f"]}